</table>
<p>The Bible asks this question, “For what shall it profit a man, if he shall gain the whole world, and lose his own soul?” (Mark 8:36) You might be debt free or even financially successful; however, the Bible states that you are in debt to God. “As it is written, There is none righteous, no, not one&#8230;For all have sinned, and come short of the glory of God;” (Romans 3:10, 23) Your debt to God must be paid. </p>
<p>+ Plus, listen to Newsboys singing &#8220;I Am Free&#8221;</p>
