		<title>GLMX #94: The Damascus Road to Heaven</title>
		<link>http://gospellightminutex.com/2012/04/glmx-94-the-damascus-road-to-heaven/</link>
		<comments>http://gospellightminutex.com/2012/04/glmx-94-the-damascus-road-to-heaven/#comments</comments>
